VM-Container
============

## Required packages
* openssl, openssl-devel
* openvpn
* tunctl
* fail2ban

## Installation checklist
* Install OpenVPN
* Setup oneadmin account
* Add oneadmin to passwordless sudoers
* turn off requiretty in sudoers
* Setup OpenVPN
* Create /datastores with chmod 777
* Export NFS /datastores
* Update iptables rules (through frontend firewall sync)
* Turn off NetworkManager
* Turn on all related services (openvpn)